# {{ project_name }} — Seeknal Project

This project uses [Seeknal](https://github.com/mta-tech/seeknal), a data engineering platform for building data pipelines, feature stores, and ML workflows.

## Quick Reference

```bash
# Core workflow: draft → validate → apply → run
seeknal draft source my_source          # Generate source template
seeknal dry-run draft_source_my_source.yml  # Validate before applying
seeknal apply draft_source_my_source.yml    # Move to project
seeknal plan                            # Preview execution order
seeknal run                             # Execute pipeline

# Explore data
seeknal repl                            # Interactive SQL shell
seeknal inspect transform.my_node       # Preview node output
seeknal lineage --ascii                 # Show DAG as ASCII tree
seeknal lineage transform.X --column Y  # Column-level lineage
```

